&lt;p&gt;An exciting opportunity has arrisen as part of our long term strategy and commitment to workforce development to employ Trainee Nursing Associates within the medicine division. We have an established history of successful trainees and legacy qualified nursing associates who have and will work across a broad variety of surgical specialities in the disvion, the size of a small hospital. We are commitee to providing bespoke support through out network of clinical educators and practice develepment nursing staff along with a true belief that this workforce is integral to excellent patient care in conjunction with the Multi-disciplinary team already in place. Come along and talk to us in Surgery about the vast array of opportunities and join our team.&lt;/p&gt;
